Cheong Kong invests $ 108 m in China road . Hong Kong ' s Cheung Kong Group will invest 895 million yuan ( $ 108 million ) to build a ring road around China ' s northeastern city of Shenyang , Chinese officials said on Wednesday . Cheung Kong Group , whose flagship company is Cheung Kong Holdings Ltd and includes Cheung Kong Infrastructure Holdings Ltd , would hold a 52 percent stake in the ring road said an official from the project ' s Chinese partner . 
